B
A = \{ [n\sqrt{2}]\mid n \in \mathbb{N}^* \}
B = \{ [n(2+\sqrt{2})]\mid n \in \mathbb{N}^* \}.
x
x
m,n\in\mathbb{N^*}
[n\sqrt{2}]=[(2+\sqrt{2})m]=t\in\mathbb{N^*}.
t<n\sqrt{2}<n+1,\quad t<(2+\sqrt{2})m<t+1\implies \dfrac{t}{\sqrt{2}}<n<\dfrac{t+1}{\sqrt{2}},\quad \dfrac{t}{2+\sqrt{2}}<m<\dfrac{t+1}{2+\sqrt{2}}\stackrel{(+)}{\implies} t<n+m<t+1,\;\text{false}\implies A\cap B=\emptyset.
